                <label>adamantine blocks</label>
                <description>Blocks of solid adamant, a rare and valuable stone. The hardest stone avaiable on this rimworld. Quite beautiful as well. The material is difficult to build with, but the resulting structures will be very strong. The origins of adamant are a mystery.</description>
